OL,3,CEx-GP jailed for sex offences against
OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,FA former GP has been jailed for sex
OL,7,Foffences after conducting unnecessary
OL,8,Fgenital examinations on male patients
OL,9,Fincluding two teenage boys.
OL,11,FGregory Manson, 56, was sentenced at
OL,12,FCanterbury Crown Court on Friday (4
OL,13,FJuly) to seven years' imprisonment for
OL,14,F16 offences including conducting groin
OL,15,Fexams even when his patients came in
OL,16,Fwith coughs, headaches, back pain and
OL,17,Fknee sprains.
