OL,3,CEx-GP jailed for sex offences against
OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,FSome of the nine victims of Manson,
OL,7,Fwho qualified as a GP in 1998 and
OL,8,Fworked in Canterbury before being
OL,9,Fdismissed in 2017, said he pulled down
OL,10,Ftheir underwear without asking their
OL,11,Fpermission.
OL,13,FJudge Simon Taylor KC told Manson that
OL,14,Fhe had "camouflaged sexual abuse in
OL,15,Fthe context of medical examinations",
OL,16,Fadding he had committed "nearly two
OL,17,Fdecades' worth of offending".
