OL,6,FDelivering his sentencing remarks,
OL,7,FJudge Taylor added: "For almost the
OL,8,Fentirety of your medical career, you
OL,9,Fperiodically and opportunistically
OL,10,Fabused male patients.
OL,12,F"Because you decided to deploy your
OL,13,Fabuse in a medical fashion, some of
OL,14,Fthese men did not know that you were
OL,15,Ftouching them for your own sexual
OL,16,Fpurposes ` it must not be forgotten
OL,17,Fyour actions victimised them."
