OL,3,CEx-GP jailed for sex offences against
OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,FManson, of Tower Way, Canterbury,
OL,7,Fdenied 18 offences of sexual assault
OL,8,Fand six of indecent assault in respect
OL,9,Fof nine victims.
OL,11,FHe was convicted on Thursday (3 July)
OL,12,Fof 12 sexual assaults and four
OL,13,Findecent assaults against nine men,
OL,14,Fwhich took place over almost two
OL,15,Fdecades.
OL,17,FHe was found not guilty of six
OL,18,Foffences, and two others were
OL,19,Falternative charges which did not
OL,20,Frequire verdicts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
