OL,3,CEx-GP jailed for sex offences against
OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,FOne of Manson's victims read out a
OL,7,Fpersonal impact statement in court on
OL,8,FFriday, in which he said he "never now
OL,9,Fvisits the GP".
OL,11,FThe victim added: "What still stuns me
OL,12,Fis how normal you made all of this
OL,13,Fseem.
OL,15,F"It was calculated, it was deliberate
OL,16,Fand we now know it was abuse. You
OL,17,Fbuilt a wall of goodwill around
OL,18,Fyourself and then used it as a shield.
OL,20,F"You don't get to hide behind your
OL,21,Ftitle anymore.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
