OL,3,CEx-GP jailed for sex offences against
OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,F"In truth Dr Manson took frequent
OL,7,Fopportunities to examine patients'
OL,8,Fgenitals, not because he needed to but
OL,9,Fbecause he wanted to," said Jennifer
OL,10,FKnight KC, prosecuting.
OL,12,FWill Bodiam from the Crown Prosecution
OL,13,FService said: "These patients trusted
OL,14,FManson as he was their GP and he
OL,15,Fabused that trust in an appalling way,
OL,16,Fcarrying out intimate examinations
OL,17,Fwhich were not all medically justified.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
