OL,6,F"They described their discomfort at
OL,7,Fwhat happened to them and some of them
OL,8,Factively tried to avoid seeing Manson
OL,9,Fbecause of their previous experiences
OL,10,Fwith him.
OL,12,F"On several occasions, the victims
OL,13,Fwere not even given the option to
OL,14,Fconsent to the examinations and had
OL,15,Ftheir underwear removed with no
OL,16,Fwarning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
