OL,4,Cpatients including two teenage boys
OL,6,F"Manson never explained to the
OL,7,Fpatients what he was doing and why,
OL,8,Ffailing to offer them the opportunity
OL,9,Fto have a chaperone and not even
OL,10,Frecording the examinations he had
OL,11,Fundertaken or any findings from them
OL,12,Fin the patient notes. This is not what
OL,13,Fpatients should expect from their GPs."
